genresAdvancedInfo.name: 528hz
genresAdvancedInfo.description: 528hz is a type of music that is believed to have healing properties. It is created using a frequency of 528hz, which is said to resonate with the heart chakra and promote feelings of love, peace, and harmony. This genre of music is often used in meditation, yoga, and other spiritual practices.
